{"tid":36280,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民族黨召集人陳浩天及發言人周浩輝於台灣遇襲","createTime":"2016-12-12T15:01:53.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-13T00:34:09.000Z","uid":319,"like":0,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7a80beb35e870cbde7dd8a199f8b64394c414c0a","tid":36280,"uid":319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T15:01:53.000Z","msg":"【召集人陳浩天及發言人周浩輝於台灣遇襲】<br />\n<br />\n敝黨召集人陳浩天及發言人周浩輝今日(12/12)晚上於台北一餐廳接受記者訪問後，當二人準備離開餐廳，多人即衝前施襲，並在場高叫「搞港獨台獨」、「漢奸賣國」。民族黨強烈譴責施襲者及其背後相關團體。二人並無大礙，現於台北中正區一警察局錄取口供，稍後將進一步交代詳情。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hknationalparty/posts/580288865503405\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhknationalparty%2Fposts%2F580288865503405&d=ihz1EdSmBbkfL291Z%2BBk%2FEsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=301aea9c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hknationalparty/posts/580288865503405</a>"},{"pid":"398968abc11c8fc188a751001b2232b5317ea325","tid":36280,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T15:03:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56db860ab3eb6163c52cea07674d32a58a89f57c","tid":36280,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T15:03:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sh